Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么难的初试  你居然满分通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加纳慎一先生真是经过千锤百炼的阿宅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.91,0:00:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本是个家里蹲  而且是一个人居住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会家里蹲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为被青梅竹马甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有前途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说我都已经快放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你这么符合条件的人才竟然能来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  贵社具体从事的业务是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上会仔细说明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前先让我们干杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太兴奋了  嗓子都干了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.89,0:01:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  为了日本的未来干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  关于我刚才提问的贵社具体从事的业务…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想过要和小慎交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否问一下为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  小慎是阿宅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.91,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿宅有什么错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没见到过的天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女仆出现啦
